photos of the site in question. Group communication was increasingly common in companies today to facilitate collaboration and exchanges between teams in the field. Ultra-resistant, waterproof, with great autonomy and usable with gloves or wet fingers, Crosscall devices were described as the allies of all those who evolved in complicated and challenging environments such as professionals in construction, manufacturing, and logistics.  With the Walkie Talkie app in Teams and Crosscall , frontline workers had access to clear, secure, and easy-to-use voice communication. BUSINESS REPORT